title: Kumail Nanjiani returns
description: KUMAIL NANJIANI (Letterman! Comedy! The FIRST YMIW Guest!) comes back to discuss so so so many things. Toothpicks, love, comedy, faith, all of it. It's all in here. Just a great and wonderful, special episode. If you enjoy it half as much as Pete did, you're going to lose your minds. HOORAY WEIRDOS!! Come see us tape our ONE HOUR COMEDY CENTRAL specials in Austin on October 23rd and 24th! Be there, please!! I promise a good time, possibly a hug. YES!
